{"tid":1420323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"！！！荃灣捉鬼！！！","createTime":"2019-08-06T04:16:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T02:58:40.000Z","uid":138291,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2f9bb41ff1160afb6aeaa98e4cba5e95b706e3a5","tid":1420323,"uid":138291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:16:46.000Z","msg":"屌你老母琴日帶頭話走走走係邊撚個嚟？on9我鬼影都見唔撚到隻，點支煙就全世界鳩跑，家陣走難定革命呀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對唔住我係標題黨，但真係要反省下到底做緊乜。我地出嚟行係要有成果，要衝擊到狗，唔好比佢地搓圓㩒扁我地。咁所以一定唔可以自亂陣腳，唔可以咁驚接刃戰。琴日7區我覺得其實未必有咁多狗力，當然唔係話一定好少人我地一擁而上就砌死晒班雜種狗，但係係咪可以睇清楚少少睇到人數先決定去留，而唔係一有狗就全場鳩跑當前線義士condom咁拋棄？<br />\n<br />\n唔係想批鬥你地，但真係要進步下，知道自己係要對抗狗隻，而唔係臣服喺警暴嘅積威之下。"},{"pid":"9350a6cfe237f887973e289ee8e0f80de243ebfe","tid":1420323,"uid":138291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:17:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"79a6642c1eaab608990f145aa6c5a6d63fa9a2c2","tid":1420323,"uid":138291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:17:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"36b52b9819c8007277bca812d9449b67ecf6f6a6","tid":1420323,"uid":138291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:17:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3e8e6d23dd22dc1f1c51298a0166af43273749da","tid":1420323,"uid":138291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:17:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"75f25c462630ec4bde3e572be391e759919dab2a","tid":1420323,"uid":138291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"